The following actions are available in the Settings menu on the Outline view toolbarView Menu on the Outline view action bar:
Filter returns exact matches The text filter of the Outline view returns only exact matches;
Selection update on cursor move Controls the synchronization between Outline view and source document. The selection in the Outline view can be synchronized with the cursor moves or the changes in the XSLT editor. Selecting one of the components from the Outline view also selects the corresponding item in the source document.
